data.description: Wonderful well kept and updated home close to post. The exterior of this 3 bedroom home has recently been redone with new siding and roof. Inside the floors have luxury plank vinyl throughout with ceramic tile in the kitchen and bath. There's a large corner lot all surrounded by a wood privacy fence plus an attached garage. Other amenities include a new water heater, new garage door and some updated insulated windows. This is a great house that's close to everything. Call Barry Ezerski @ 580-704-7355 to see it today.
